<text top="311" left="113" width="246" height="11" font="2"><b>PRST 51/1. Reports of the Advisory Committee </b></text>
<text top="337" left="142" width="286" height="9" font="1">At  the  40th  meeting,  held  on  6  October  2022,  the  President  of  the </text>
<text top="349" left="113" width="219" height="9" font="1">Human Rights Council made the following statement: </text>
<text top="365" left="170" width="257" height="11" font="1">“The Human Rights Council, recalling its resolutions 5/1 of 18 </text>
<text top="379" left="142" width="286" height="9" font="1">June 2007 and 16/21 of 25 March 2011, in particular section III of the </text>
<text top="391" left="142" width="283" height="9" font="1">annexes thereto, including on the functions of the Advisory Committee,</text>
<text top="391" left="425" width="2" height="9" font="5"><i> </i></text>
<text top="403" left="142" width="284" height="9" font="1">takes  note  of  the  reports  of  the  Advisory  Committee  on  its  twenty-</text>
<text top="415" left="142" width="152" height="9" font="1">seventh  and  twenty-eighth  sessions,</text>
<text top="414" left="294" width="3" height="5" font="6">1</text>
<text top="415" left="297" width="130" height="9" font="1">  and  notes  that  the  Advisory </text>
<text top="427" left="142" width="183" height="9" font="1">Committee has made four research proposals.</text>
<text top="426" left="325" width="3" height="5" font="6">2</text>
<text top="425" left="328" width="7" height="11" font="1">” </text>
